1. I can see that there is an "Interest Receivable" line item
2. The initial amount for this account as of 2023-12-31 is 0.00
3. The end amount for this account as of 2024-02-01 is 9066.78

This "Interest Receivable" represents interest that has been earned but not yet received, which is exactly what the task is asking for.
